App Name: ThonMatch

App Type: AI-powered cultural dating platform for South Sudanese singles

Core Features:
1. User Sign Up and Profile Creation
   - Collect name, age, gender, location (diaspora/home), tribe, dialect, religion, family values.
   - Use OpenAI to auto-generate a dating bio based on cultural inputs.

2. Matchmaking Engine
   - Filter matches by preferences (tribe, religion, values).
   - Display profiles in Tinder-style card format.

3. AI Icebreaker Generator
   - On profile view, show 3 AI-generated cultural icebreakers based on shared values or location.

4. In-App Chat with AI Coach
   - Use ChatGPT to offer dating advice inside chat window.
   - Commands: “Help me reply”, “Suggest a date idea”.

5. Admin Dashboard
   - View registered users.
   - Moderate bios and chat reports.

Tech Stack:
- Frontend: React.js (or Bubble for no-code)
- Backend: Node.js or Firebase
- AI: OpenAI GPT API (text-davinci-003 or gpt-4)
- Database: Firestore or Supabase
- Hosting: Vercel or Netlify

Design:
- Minimal, mobile-first layout.
- Traditional patterns/colors for a South Sudanese aesthetic.

Monetization:
- Free version + Paid “ThonPlus” tier (see who likes you, more matches per day).

Launch Strategy:
- Target diaspora first (USA, Australia, Canada, Kenya, Uganda).
- Use TikTok/Instagram reels featuring relatable skits.
